;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504013001: Config/Level/Mission/5040130/Act/Act504013001.json-->
::'''Xenia:''' ...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Hello!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I want to take a bath!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013004-->
::'''Xenia:''' ...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Anyone there?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Hey, don't ignore me...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013007-->
::'''Xenia:''' Ah, apologies, good guest. I was distracted. You are... I've heard about you before &mdash; the warrior from foreign lands who fights side by side with Chrysos Heirs, am I correct?
::'''Xenia:''' Welcome to Marmoreal Palace, good guest. Lady Aglaea has instructed us to receive you and your fine companions as esteemed guests.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Any perks that come with that?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013010-->
:::'''Xenia:''' Of course. Lady Aglaea must have told you about this place, but allow me to give you a thorough introduction...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} But you just ignored me.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013012-->
:::'''Xenia:''' My sincerest apologies, good guest. My thoughts wandered out of the Gate of Infinity just now, I absolutely did not mean to ignore you.
:::'''Xenia:''' Rather, if you don't mind, I would hope to converse further with you, and listen to your tales outside the city.
:::'''Xenia:''' These matters aside, Lady Aglaea should have briefed you about this place. Please allow me to elaborate on the privileges you possess.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504013015-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013015-->
::'''Xenia:''' You can enter and exit the bath anytime, use the bath's various facilities free of charge, and enjoy exclusive discounts on paid amenities, though this offer does not extend to some products.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's amazing!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013017-->
:::'''Xenia:''' Allowing people to wash off their taint and attain serenity &mdash; that's the original purpose of the Marmoreal Palace. The warriors who assisted in defending Okhema are even more worthy of commendation, so it is only natural that we provide the respective services.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why isn't it all free?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013019-->
:::'''Xenia:''' Sincerest apologies, but the staff here also need to earn a living... Also, it does not reflect well on Talanton's teachings if a good intention goes astray.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504013020-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013020-->
::'''Xenia:''' As for the reading room, pool restaurant and other amenities... Hmm, I'd better leave their introductions to my bath coworkers.
::'''Xenia:''' This is all I have to say. You may go in and have a look around as you please. I will proceed to daydream here and snap back to reality if you need me.
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504013002: Config/Level/Mission/5040130/Act/Act504013002.json-->
::'''Xenia:''' ...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Daydreaming again?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Helloooo...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013094-->
::'''Xenia:''' Apologies, this way to enter... Ah, it is you, my good guest. Glad to see you again, how may I help you?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
:{{DIcon}} I want to buy something.
::'''Xenia:''' That's no problem, but the city has recently undergone some changes, and we have a limited selection of merchandise. Let's see... We currently have these for sale. I can introduce them in detail if you're interested.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504013005_87-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504013005_87-->
:;(If {{Mission|Night Stars, Accompany My Slumber|showChapter=0}} has been completed)
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Light Calendar Membership
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013213-->
:::;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 304002018-->)
:::::'''Xenia:''' If you intend to be a regular at our baths, a membership is surely the wisest choice.
:::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} But my VIP privileges...
:::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Isn't it free to enter the baths?
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013217-->
:::::'''Xenia:''' Ah, please do not misunderstand, membership does not include discounts or membership points. Simply put, this payment is akin to a gift for Phagousa...
:::::'''Xenia:''' ...Truth be told, Marmoreal Palace's bath was not meant to be free in the beginning &mdash; we employed the pay-as-you-go policy. The designer may have their reasons behind this but it felt more like a scam to our guests when they were asked to pay.
:::::'''Xenia:''' No one ever brought this matter up later on, but we still kept the payment channel &mdash; this is the true meaning of the membership. Which is why you will have the respect of all bath staff if you join our membership!
:::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So that's what it is, huh?
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013221-->
::::::'''Xenia:''' Yes.
:::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's it?
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013223-->
::::::'''Xenia:''' That's it.
:::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504013224-->
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013224-->
:::::'''Xenia:''' If I may... Would you like to join our membership?
:::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll join up!
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013226-->
