::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504013003_55-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504013003_55-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Why are you always in a daze when I see you?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013103-->
:::'''Xenia:''' Because of the waterfall.
:::'''Xenia:''' ...Should I... elaborate?
:::'''Xenia:''' Just as the artists say, the eternal night that Oronyx symbolizes is a thing most suited to spark the inspiration of creation. And to me, the thing that stimulates my thoughts is this &mdash; Marmoreal Palace's waterfall.
:::'''Xenia:''' Myriad knotted thoughts will undo themselves when I listen to its constant splashing barrage. The only price I have to pay is the manager's constant yammering: "Keep slacking off and Thanatos shall take you away."
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} How's work?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013108-->
:::'''Xenia:''' It's all right. The previous attack has had some effect, but everything else is fine. It's just... we need to be more watchful with guests who are warriors or guards in some capacity.
:::'''Xenia:''' From what I've noticed, there has been a rise in guests with minor injuries coming for a soak, as well as a downturn of regular customers... I hope they are all right.
:::'''Xenia:''' But... I believe that this is temporary. Okhema's people have always been hardy, and so will the future &mdash; may Kephale protect us.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell me about the baths.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013112-->
:::'''Xenia:''' Mm, it somewhat terrifies me that I am to elaborate on Lady Aglaea's words... I shall tell you about matters that only staff are privy to then.
:::'''Xenia:''' We claim that the Marmoreal Palace's history dates back to several thousand Light Calendar years, but its history is technically shorter than that. The fact that it's younger than as claimed has only highlighted the talent of its builders.
:::'''Xenia:''' As for the baths themselves, apart from the central pool, the water in the other pools is no ordinary water, but mixed with substances that nourish the body, such as bath salts, milk, and Phagousa's ambrosia, among other things.
:::'''Xenia:''' They all offer different effects, and you can tell the difference from their aroma. Also... some people say that imbibing the bath water directly yields even more effective results, but I strongly suggest against that.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} No worries, I won't bother you then.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504013117-->
